
                            Contributing to WolfMUD

Contributing to WolfMUD has been made as simple as possible to encourage
submissions. There are only two requirements for submissions:

  1. You agree to license your work under the same license as WolfMUD,
     contained in the LICENSE file.

  2. You certify your work according to the Developer's Certificate of Origin,
     contained in the DCO file.

To indicate acceptance of these requirements all submissions must be
accompanied with a sign off line. For example:

  Signed-off-by: Andrew 'Diddymus' Rolfe <diddymus@wolfmud.org>

Please use your real name and email address.

